Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.11,0:00:22.73,Kingdom-Thought,Zheng,0,0,0,,It's warm... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.33,0:00:22.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（政(せい)）温かいな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.88,0:00:28.42,Kingdom-Thought,Zheng,0,0,0,,Oh... It's the first time... I've felt this warmth... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.04,0:00:28.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか　初めてだ このぬくもりは
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.38,0:00:35.69,Kingdom-Thought,Zheng,0,0,0,,This is the first time... I've been hugged by someone like this. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.44,0:00:32.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰かに\Nこうして抱きしめられるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.31,0:00:35.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,初めてだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:43.02,Kingdom-Thought,Xia,0,0,0,,I won't let them kill him... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.05,0:00:45.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（紫夏(しか)）\N殺させない　この子は私が守る
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.02,0:00:45.43,Kingdom-Thought,Xia,0,0,0,,I will protect this child! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.53,0:00:53.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（亜門(あもん)）ンンッ… まだかよ？\N紫夏のヤツ 何やってんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.28,0:00:51.84,Kingdom-Flashback,Ya,0,0,0,,They're still not back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.84,0:00:54.05,Kingdom-Flashback,Ya,0,0,0,,What is Xia doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.04,0:00:57.19,Kingdom-Flashback,Xia,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.27,0:00:59.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（紫夏）お待たせ！\N（亜門）紫夏！ 遅(おせ)えよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.19,0:00:59.18,Kingdom-Flashback,Ya,0,0,0,,That took forever, Xia!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.18,0:01:02.45,Kingdom-Flashback,Jiang,0,0,0,,Hey, is the kid okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.21,0:01:02.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（江彰(こうしょう)）\Nおい！ そのガキ 大丈夫なのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.74,0:01:04.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フフッ… 大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.60,0:01:04.70,Kingdom-Flashback,Xia,0,0,0,,He's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.28,0:01:07.80,Kingdom-Flashback,Xia,0,0,0,,He's all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.45,0:01:07.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（紫夏）もう大丈夫
