Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.10,0:01:33.91,Kingdom-Flashback,Narrator,0,0,0,,The young boy, Zheng, fated from birth to become king, is being delivered to the State of Qin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.37,0:01:31.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）大王となる宿命のもとに\N生まれた少年 政を―
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.37,0:01:33.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,秦国(しんこく)に送り届ける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.81,0:01:37.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,紫夏と その一行は\N趙国(ちょうこく)の最後の関門を抜け
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.91,0:01:37.66,Kingdom-Flashback,Narrator,0,0,0,,Zi Xia and her band of black marketeers had just gotten through the last gate of the State of Zhao,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.58,0:01:40.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一路 国境へと馬を走らせていた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.66,0:01:40.99,Kingdom-Flashback,Narrator,0,0,0,,and were running on horseback straight to the state border.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.99,0:01:43.20,Kingdom-Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,Okay! Okay! We're gonna make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.18,0:01:44.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（田慈(でんじ)）よし！ よし！\N帰れる 秦国に帰れるぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.20,0:01:44.74,Kingdom-Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,We're gonna make it to the State of Qin!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.82,0:01:49.25,Kingdom-Thought,Jiang,0,0,0,,From running non-stop for days, the horses are pretty tired. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.82,0:01:49.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,連日 走ってるせいで\N馬も かなり疲れてやがる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.70,0:01:53.25,Kingdom-Thought,Xia,0,0,0,,That really did waste a lot of time... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.09,0:01:53.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さっきの時間の浪費が\Nやはり大きかったか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.48,0:01:56.51,Kingdom-Thought,Ya,0,0,0,,The State of Zhao has the best pursuers in all of China. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.66,0:01:56.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（亜門）趙国の追尾能力は中華一だ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.46,0:01:59.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もし俺たちのことが\Nバレてるとしたら そろそろ…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.51,0:01:59.92,Kingdom-Thought,Ya,0,0,0,,If they did find out about is, then it won't be long... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.76,0:02:06.28,Kingdom-Flashback,Ya,0,0,0,,A sand cloud!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.77,0:02:08.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,砂煙だ！\N後方で砂煙が上がっている！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.28,0:02:08.42,Kingdom-Flashback,Ya,0,0,0,,There's a sand cloud rising from the path behind us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.42,0:02:09.77,Kingdom-Flashback,Ya,0,0,0,,It's the mounted unit that's been pursuing us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.44,0:02:11.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,追っ手の騎馬隊だ！\N（道剣(どうけん)）なに？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.03,0:02:11.27,Kingdom-Flashback,Dao,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.38,0:02:13.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（単元(たんげん)）クッ… ここまで来て…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.04,0:02:13.78,Kingdom-Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,They've already caught up this much?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.78,0:02:16.52,Kingdom-Flashback,Xia,0,0,0,,Don't panic! They're still quite a ways behind us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.88,0:02:16.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,慌てるな！ まだ だいぶ後ろだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.77,0:02:18.78,Kingdom-Flashback,Xia,0,0,0,,Ready the weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.88,0:02:20.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,武器の準備をしろ！\N戦いながらの逃走になるぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.78,0:02:21.03,Kingdom-Flashback,Xia,0,0,0,,We're going to fight while fleeing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.24,0:02:27.00,Kingdom-Flashback,Xia,0,0,0,,Lord Dao Jian, where is the rendezvous point?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.46,0:02:29.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,道剣どの 合流地は？\N（道剣）松で囲まれた池のほとりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:29.54,Kingdom-Flashback,Dao,0,0,0,,The bank of a pond surrounded by pine trees!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.56,0:02:32.04,Kingdom-Flashback,Xia,0,0,0,,Chisong Pond?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.60,0:02:31.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,赤松(あかまつ)の池か
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.04,0:02:33.83,Kingdom-Thought,Ya,0,0,0,,That's too far! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.23,0:02:36.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,遠すぎる　赤松は国境の向こう側だ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.83,0:02:36.29,Kingdom-Thought,Ya,0,0,0,,Chisong is on the other side of the state border! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.64,0:02:37.97,Kingdom-Thought,Jiang,0,0,0,,It can't be done. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.74,0:02:40.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ムリだ\Nそこまで騎馬隊からは逃げられん
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.97,0:02:40.02,Kingdom-Thought,Jiang,0,0,0,,We'll never evade the mounted unit all the way there! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.41,0:02:44.44,Kingdom-Flashback,Jiang,0,0,0,,Ya Men!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.64,0:02:45.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（江彰）亜門！\N（亜門）おう！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.44,0:02:45.30,Kingdom-Flashback,Ya,0,0,0,,Yeah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.50,0:02:50.81,Kingdom-Flashback,Jiang,0,0,0,,You haven't forgotten the promise we made when we were kids, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.65,0:02:50.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ガキんときに決めた２人の約束\N忘れてないだろうな？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.85,0:02:53.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヘッ… 忘れるかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.04,0:02:53.81,Kingdom-Flashback,Ya,0,0,0,,Like I could forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.50,0:03:05.53,Kingdom-Thought,Ya,0,0,0,,The last one of us three to die will be Zi Xia! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.66,0:03:05.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（江彰･亜門）３人の中で\Nいちばん最後に死ぬのは紫夏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.81,0:03:08.32,Kingdom-Flashback,Ya,0,0,0,,We're originally orphans that got adopted after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.93,0:03:08.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もともと拾われた命だしな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.32,0:03:12.83,Kingdom-Flashback,Ya,0,0,0,,But from the moment we became black marketeers, we had to be prepared for something like this to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.40,0:03:12.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,闇商人やってる時点で いつか\Nこうなる覚悟はしてたけどよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.15,0:03:16.90,Kingdom-Flashback,Ya,0,0,0,,The only regret I have is that I could never make her mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.37,0:03:16.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつをモノに\Nできなかったことだけが心残りだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.81,0:03:21.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,せめて告白ぐらいしとくんだった\Nタハハハッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.90,0:03:19.67,Kingdom-Flashback,Ya,0,0,0,,I wish I would've at least confessed to her at some point!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.46,0:03:23.59,Kingdom-Flashback,Jiang,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.55,0:03:24.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は したぜ\N（亜門）えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.33,0:03:27.54,Kingdom-Flashback,Jiang,0,0,0,,When I was 16, I asked her to marry me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.52,0:03:27.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,16んときに“結婚しろ”っつった
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.54,0:03:30.60,Kingdom-Flashback,Ya,0,0,0,,What?! And what happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.55,0:03:30.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なに？ そ… それで？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.60,0:03:34.65,Kingdom-Flashback,Jiang,0,0,0,,She turned me down. She said she was gonna take over for dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.62,0:03:34.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつは断って\N親父(おやじ)の後を継ぎやがった
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:37.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,プッ！\Nタハハッ… お前 フラれたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.81,0:03:38.26,Kingdom-Flashback,Ya,0,0,0,,She blew you off, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.23,0:03:40.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うるせえ！\N（亜門）…ていうか てめえ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.26,0:03:38.86,Kingdom-Flashback,Jiang,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:42.94,Kingdom-Flashback,Ya,0,0,0,,And anyhow, I'm impressed ya kept somethin' major like that from me for so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.40,0:03:42.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな大事なこと\Nよくも今まで黙ってたな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.80,0:03:45.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（江彰）うるせえ！\Nてめえなんかに言うかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.94,0:03:43.95,Kingdom-Flashback,Jiang,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.95,0:03:45.86,Kingdom-Flashback,Jiang,0,0,0,,You're not one to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.68,0:03:55.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（田慈）ハァ… ハァハァ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.39,0:04:12.14,Kingdom-Flashback,Jiang,0,0,0,,No way...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.53,0:04:12.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まさか…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.64,0:04:16.16,Kingdom-Flashback,Jiang,0,0,0,,The mounted unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.80,0:04:17.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,騎馬隊だ！ 騎馬隊がいるぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.16,0:04:17.39,Kingdom-Flashback,Jiang,0,0,0,,They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.92,0:04:23.90,Kingdom-Flashback,Jiang,0,0,0,,Run, Zi Xia!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.94,0:04:23.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逃げろ！ 紫夏！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.09,0:04:29.66,Kingdom-Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,You traitors!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.38,0:04:29.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（騎兵）この国賊が！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.91,0:04:33.91,Kingdom-Flashback,Ya,0,0,0,,Zi Xia!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:33.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,紫夏！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.13,0:04:37.48,Kingdom-Flashback,Ya,0,0,0,,Stay away from our general, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.35,0:04:38.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ウチの大将に近づくな てめえ！\N（紫夏）亜門！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.48,0:04:38.29,Kingdom-Flashback,Xia,0,0,0,,Ya Men!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.93,0:04:44.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アアッ！\N（亜門）単元！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:44.80,Kingdom-Flashback,Xia,0,0,0,,Dan Yuan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.37,0:04:50.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヘヘッ…\Nやっぱ告白しときゃよかったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.08,0:04:50.80,Kingdom-Flashback,Ya,0,0,0,,I really do wish I'd have confessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:53.93,Kingdom-Flashback,Ya,0,0,0,,Zi Xia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.74,0:04:53.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,紫夏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.12,0:04:58.06,Kingdom-Flashback,Ya,0,0,0,,So long!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:04:58.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あばよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.48,0:05:01.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ウオーッ！\N（紫夏）亜門！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:01.40,Kingdom-Flashback,Xia,0,0,0,,Ya Men!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:08.65,Kingdom-Flashback,Xia,0,0,0,,Ya Men!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.72,0:05:08.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,亜門！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.72,0:05:11.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クッ… くそー！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.53,0:05:11.91,Kingdom-Flashback,Jiang,0,0,0,,Goddammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.32,0:05:18.78,Kingdom-Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,Any sign of them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.53,0:05:18.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士）それらしい気配はないか？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.77,0:05:21.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（見張り）\N何も　砂煙ひとつ見えません
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.78,0:05:19.94,Kingdom-Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,None!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.94,0:05:21.80,Kingdom-Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,I don't see a single cloud of dust!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.80,0:05:24.28,Kingdom-Flashback,Chang,0,0,0,,Then just keep watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.90,0:05:24.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（昌文君(しょうぶんくん)）そのまま見張りを続けよ\N騎馬隊は―
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.28,0:05:27.38,Kingdom-Flashback,Chang,0,0,0,,And be prepared for a mounted unit to come at any time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.87,0:05:27.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつでも出られる準備をしておけ\N（部下）はっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.38,0:05:28.05,Kingdom-Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.22,0:05:46.77,Kingdom-Thought,Dao,0,0,0,,Is this the end? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.46,0:05:46.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（道剣）これまでか…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.85,0:06:21.08,Kingdom-Flashback,Ghosts,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.89,0:06:20.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（亡霊Ａ）どこへ行く？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.96,0:06:24.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（亡霊Ｂ）お前の居場所など\Nどこにもないぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.08,0:06:25.36,Kingdom-Flashback,Ghosts,0,0,0,,You don't belong anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:27.79,Kingdom-Flashback,Ghosts,0,0,0,,You should just go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.50,0:06:30.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（亡霊Ｄ）そのまま眠ればいい\N楽になれるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.79,0:06:29.74,Kingdom-Flashback,Ghosts,0,0,0,,Everything will feel so much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.94,0:06:34.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（政）ハァ… アアッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.38,0:06:36.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハァ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.74,0:06:49.01,Kingdom-Flashback,Shadow,0,0,0,,W-Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.85,0:06:51.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（幻影）\Nフフッ… 待てよ フフフフッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.77,0:06:54.26,Kingdom-Flashback,Shadow,0,0,0,,I know, Zheng.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.86,0:06:54.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は知っているぞ 政
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.08,0:07:00.68,Kingdom-Flashback,Shadow,0,0,0,,I know that you're a member of the royal family, who was born in an enemy state and pelted with the malice of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.40,0:07:00.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,王族の身でありながら敵国に生まれ\N戦争の怨念にあたり
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.63,0:07:05.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は\N痛みを失うほどに心は内に籠もった
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.68,0:07:05.52,Kingdom-Flashback,Shadow,0,0,0,,So much so that you shut your emotions down so deep that you lost even the ability to feel pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:11.86,Kingdom-Flashback,Shadow,0,0,0,,But you haven't become merely a soulless doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.81,0:07:11.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが お前は ただ魂の抜けた人形に\Nなっていたわけじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.84,0:07:15.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひたすら自問自答を繰り返していた
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:15.11,Kingdom-Flashback,Shadow,0,0,0,,You've been doing nothing but answering your own questions over and over...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:21.29,Kingdom-Flashback,Shadow,0,0,0,,About war, people, kingdoms, and kings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.85,0:07:18.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,戦争と人と…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:21.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,国と王について
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.39,0:07:25.34,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.59,0:07:24.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのとおりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.34,0:07:31.30,Kingdom-Flashback,Shadow,0,0,0,,And so now, you've drawn a fearsome king's path in your heart, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.43,0:07:31.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（幻影）そして今 お前は胸の中に\N恐ろしい王の道を描いているな？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:37.80,Kingdom-Flashback,Shadow,0,0,0,,A perilous road no one has ever walked before...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:37.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いまだかつて\N何者も歩んでいない恐ろしい道を
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.94,0:07:41.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フフフッ… やめておけ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.83,0:07:41.70,Kingdom-Flashback,Shadow,0,0,0,,Give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.70,0:07:46.92,Kingdom-Flashback,Shadow,0,0,0,,It would be so much easier to just sleep here with us...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.74,0:07:46.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今ここで我らと眠りに就くほうが\Nずっと楽だぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.20,0:07:50.07,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,Stop your meaningless struggling.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.48,0:07:49.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ムダなあがきは よせ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.86,0:07:55.57,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,I had sunk into the darkness, but this person has reached her hand out to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.98,0:07:55.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（政）闇に沈んでいた俺に\Nこの人は手を差し伸べてくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.23,0:07:58.37,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,Her strong hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.46,0:08:00.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（政）力強い手\Nもはや迷うことも臆することもない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:08:01.01,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,I no longer feel any hesitation or fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.00,0:08:06.83,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,I will go to the State of Qin and become king!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.06,0:08:06.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は秦国へ帰り 王となる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:17.88,Kingdom-Flashback,Shadow,0,0,0,,It will be a rigorous path that will call death towards you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:17.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,周りに死を呼ぶ過酷な道だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.88,0:08:19.99,Kingdom-Flashback,Shadow,0,0,0,,You'll suffer...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.88,0:08:19.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,苦しむぞ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.10,0:08:24.57,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,I am prepared for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.25,0:08:26.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,覚悟のうえだ　俺は必ず…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.57,0:08:26.22,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,I have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.79,0:08:38.91,Kingdom-Flashback,Xia,0,0,0,,You're awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.06,0:08:40.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お目覚めになりましたか\N（政）ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.47,0:08:40.44,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.41,0:08:45.84,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,Xia... Your arm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.57,0:08:45.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,紫夏 その腕は…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.84,0:08:49.42,Kingdom-Flashback,Xia,0,0,0,,There are stray arrows coming, so please lower your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.87,0:08:49.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,流れ矢が来ますので\N頭を下げておいてくださいね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.09,0:08:58.13,Kingdom-Flashback,Jiang,0,0,0,,You really woke up at the worst time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.25,0:08:57.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最悪のときに起きちまったな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:09:01.34,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,Dao Jian, how far is it to the rendezvous point?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.29,0:09:03.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,道剣 合流地までは？\N（道剣）恐らく およそ二刻(ふたこく)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.34,0:09:03.95,Kingdom-Flashback,Dao,0,0,0,,Most likely about two ke.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.34,0:09:08.60,Kingdom-TL Note,TL Note,0,0,0,,( A "ke" is about 15 minutes. )
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.92,0:09:08.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし 恐れながら\Nあと半刻と もちそうにありません
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.95,0:09:08.60,Kingdom-Flashback,Dao,0,0,0,,But I fear we may not be able to last another quarter ke.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.89,0:09:11.86,Kingdom-Flashback,Jiang,0,0,0,,If the mounted unit catches us, it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.10,0:09:11.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,騎馬隊に捕まっちまったら\Nどうしようもねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.10,0:09:15.12,Kingdom-Flashback,Jiang,0,0,0,,It's hard to accept, but I think this is the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.20,0:09:14.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（江彰）悔しいが これまでだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.94,0:09:19.61,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,Don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.04,0:09:19.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,諦めるな！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.36,0:09:25.95,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,We're not out of arrows and our horses are still running!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.61,0:09:28.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,矢も尽きていない　馬も走っている\Nまだ うなだれるときではないぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.95,0:09:28.41,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,It's not time to be hanging our heads yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:32.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今は １歩でも\N秦国に近づくことだけを考えろ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.41,0:09:32.50,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,What we have to be thinking about is getting as close to the State of Qin as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.86,0:09:35.39,Kingdom-Thought,Jiang,0,0,0,,What's with this kid all of a sudden? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.05,0:09:35.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だ？ こいつ　いきなり…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.69,0:09:38.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うむ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.22,0:09:44.24,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,Zi Xia, there's a chance that the soldiers at the rendezvous point might be coming this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.26,0:09:43.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,紫夏 合流地の兵が\N動いてくる可能性だってある
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.20,0:09:47.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,早々に諦めるなんて\Nお前らしくないぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.24,0:09:47.27,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,It's not like you to give up so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.28,0:09:51.02,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,You said you were gonna bring me to the State of Qin, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.30,0:09:50.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺を秦国へ連れていくと\N言っただろう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.91,0:09:55.02,Kingdom-Flashback,Xia,0,0,0,,Sounds like you really have woken up, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.10,0:09:54.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当に目覚められたみたいですね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.36,0:09:58.28,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,It's all because you extended your hand out to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.64,0:09:57.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前が\N手を差し伸べてくれたおかげだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.75,0:10:08.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（天布(てんふ)）ハハハッ… いきなり\N張り切りだしましたぞ あの男
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.86,0:10:08.29,Kingdom-Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,That man's suddenly gotten really enthusiastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.32,0:10:14.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（冬顔(とうがん)）フフッ… 秦国の山猿が\N我らの力を見せてやろう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.27,0:10:11.76,Kingdom-Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,Damn State of Qin monkeys.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.76,0:10:14.66,Kingdom-Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,Let me show you our power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.66,0:10:16.04,Kingdom-Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,All archers, fire at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.69,0:10:18.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一点掃射！\N（騎兵たち）オーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.51,0:10:23.01,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,Dao Jian.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.77,0:10:23.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,道剣！\N（矢の刺さる音）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.66,0:10:29.77,Kingdom-Flashback,Dao,0,0,0,,I-I'm chagrined...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.27,0:10:29.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,む… 無念
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.77,0:10:33.40,Kingdom-Flashback,Dao,0,0,0,,L-Lord Zheng, forgive me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.08,0:10:33.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,せ… 政さま お許しを…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.66,0:10:35.15,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,Dao Jian!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.85,0:10:35.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,道剣！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.27,0:10:42.86,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.29,0:10:42.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くそ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.82,0:10:46.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（幻影）周りに死を呼ぶ過酷な道だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.86,0:10:46.29,Kingdom-Thought,Shadow,0,0,0,,It will be a rigorous path that will call death towards you... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.34,0:10:49.66,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.58,0:10:55.79,Kingdom - Episode Title,Xia,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,0)\be1\fs70\an8\pos(832.4,319.4)}Zi Xia
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.37,0:10:55.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くそー！\N（床を殴る音）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.28,0:11:04.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん？ あれは…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.33,0:11:04.28,Kingdom-Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,Hm? That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.55,0:11:06.43,Kingdom-Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,Reporting!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.82,0:11:06.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（見張り）報告！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.03,0:11:22.14,Kingdom-Flashback,Fat,0,0,0,,We knocked off all of those State of Qin guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.13,0:11:24.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,秦国のヤツらは全て倒した\Nあとは商人２人と政のみ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.14,0:11:24.61,Kingdom-Flashback,Fat,0,0,0,,Now all that's left are the two merchants and Zheng!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.93,0:11:28.62,Kingdom-Flashback,Fat,0,0,0,,We'll rip those two traitors limb from limb and put them on display!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.07,0:11:28.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（冬顔）国賊２人は\N八つ裂きにして野にさらせ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.62,0:11:32.72,Kingdom-Flashback,Fat,0,0,0,,We'll bring back Zheng's head, so don't harm his face!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.74,0:11:30.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,政は首を持ち帰る！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.01,0:11:35.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,顔は傷つけるな\N胴より下は ２人と同様だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.72,0:11:35.37,Kingdom-Flashback,Fat,0,0,0,,Treat anything below his neck the same as those two!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.39,0:11:52.42,Kingdom-Thought,Xia,0,0,0,,Father, just like how you saved us, {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.39,0:11:48.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,父上…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.33,0:11:52.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたが我々を救ってくれたように
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.36,0:11:55.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私も\Nこの子を救おうと思ったのですが
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.42,0:11:55.83,Kingdom-Thought,Xia,0,0,0,,I thought I could save this boy, but... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.39,0:11:58.08,Kingdom-Thought,Xia,0,0,0,,It seems so hard. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.44,0:11:58.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,難しそうです
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.48,0:12:02.88,Kingdom-Thought,Xia,0,0,0,,I overestimated my own power... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.70,0:12:02.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分の力を過信していた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.88,0:12:05.24,Kingdom-Thought,Xia,0,0,0,,and got Ya Men and Jiang Zhang involved... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.94,0:12:05.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,亜門と江彰を巻き込んで…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.15,0:12:11.16,Kingdom-Thought,Xia,0,0,0,,I guess saving a person's life isn't that simple. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.24,0:12:10.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やはり 人の命を救うことは\Nそんなに簡単ではない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.20,0:12:16.70,Kingdom-Thought,Xia,0,0,0,,Now that Ya Men sacrificed himself, I don't feel like I can save anyone anymore. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.28,0:12:16.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,亜門が犠牲になった今\N自分が助かろうなんて思いません
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.08,0:12:21.22,Kingdom-Thought,Xia,0,0,0,,But if I can at least just save this boy... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.12,0:12:21.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だけど せめて この子だけでも…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.22,0:12:25.67,Kingdom-Thought,Xia,0,0,0,,If I can connect this life you gave me to another... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.29,0:12:25.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いただいた命を次につなげなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.47,0:12:32.95,Kingdom-Thought,Xia,0,0,0,,A sand cloud! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.50,0:12:33.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（紫夏）砂煙！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.44,0:12:39.74,Kingdom-Flashback,Chang,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.48,0:12:40.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,急げ！ 必ず政さまを―
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.74,0:12:43.50,Kingdom-Flashback,Chang,0,0,0,,We must bring Lord Zheng to Xiangyang at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.01,0:12:44.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,咸陽(かんよう)まで お連れするのだ！\N（部下たち）はっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.50,0:12:44.44,Kingdom-Flashback,Guys,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.54,0:12:48.71,Kingdom-Flashback,Xia,0,0,0,,Lord Zheng, please lend me a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.75,0:12:50.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,政さま 御をお願いします\Nしっかり手綱を持って
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.71,0:12:50.36,Kingdom-Flashback,Xia,0,0,0,,Hold on to the reins tightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.52,0:12:53.04,Kingdom-Flashback,Xia,0,0,0,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.52,0:12:54.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいですか？\N御には集中が必要です
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:55.08,Kingdom-Flashback,Xia,0,0,0,,You will need heavy concentration for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.08,0:12:58.35,Kingdom-Flashback,Xia,0,0,0,,So make sure not to look behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.29,0:12:58.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶対に 後ろを見ないように
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.22,0:13:01.83,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,Zi Xia, what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.23,0:13:01.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,紫夏 何をする気だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.13,0:13:04.84,Kingdom-Flashback,Xia,0,0,0,,We'll give everything we have to the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.27,0:13:04.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（紫夏）最後まで力を尽くすんです
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.23,0:13:07.84,Kingdom-Flashback,Xia,0,0,0,,And never give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.37,0:13:07.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,諦めずに
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.98,0:13:12.56,Kingdom-Thought,Zheng,0,0,0,,Zi Xia! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.04,0:13:12.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,紫夏…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.48,0:13:14.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハッ… あれは…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.56,0:13:15.10,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,Ah, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.49,0:13:18.95,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,The soldiers from the rendezvous point are heading this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.55,0:13:18.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,合流地の兵が向かってきている
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.85,0:13:21.33,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,Can we make it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.99,0:13:21.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（政）間に合うか？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.26,0:13:25.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ウッ！\N（紫夏）江彰！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.92,0:13:25.98,Kingdom-Flashback,Xia,0,0,0,,Jiang Zhang!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.56,0:13:33.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,亜門みてえに\Nカッコよくは逝(い)けねえみてえだな…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:33.16,Kingdom-Flashback,Jiang,0,0,0,,Looks like I'm not going out in a cool way like Ya Men did...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:35.40,Kingdom-Flashback,Jiang,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.20,0:13:35.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,けど…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.26,0:13:42.41,Kingdom-Flashback,Jiang,0,0,0,,For an orphaned life that was saved, this is plenty...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.30,0:13:41.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,拾われた命にしちゃ 上出来だ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.31,0:13:46.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最後まで\Nホレた女のそばにいられたからよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.41,0:13:46.38,Kingdom-Flashback,Jiang,0,0,0,,because I was able to be with the woman I loved to the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.05,0:13:50.76,Kingdom-Flashback,Jiang,0,0,0,,Zi Xia! Stay alive as long as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.21,0:13:50.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,紫夏！ 少しでも長く生きろよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.36,0:13:52.76,Kingdom-Flashback,Xia,0,0,0,,Jiang Zhang!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.45,0:13:52.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,江彰！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.22,0:13:59.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,江彰ーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.31,0:13:59.64,Kingdom-Flashback,Xia,0,0,0,,Jiang Zhang!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.06,0:14:23.29,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:23.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くそ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.47,0:14:28.55,Kingdom-Flashback,Xia,0,0,0,,I'm sorry... Jiang Zhang... Ya Men...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.48,0:14:28.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（紫夏）ごめん 江彰 亜門…\N（泣き声）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.40,0:14:32.37,Kingdom-Flashback,Xia,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I dragged the two of you into this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.49,0:14:32.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私が２人を巻き込んでしまった
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.30,0:14:37.81,Kingdom-Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.43,0:14:40.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よ～し　あとは政と女１人だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.81,0:14:40.31,Kingdom-Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,Now all that's left are Zheng and the woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.97,0:14:44.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私も すぐに…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.98,0:14:44.44,Kingdom-Thought,Xia,0,0,0,,I'll be with you soon... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:51.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（騎兵）ハハハハッ…\Nあの女 細腕で弓を引くつもりか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.52,0:14:52.20,Kingdom-Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,Does that woman think she can use a bow with those slender arms?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.64,0:14:55.70,Kingdom-Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,That woman's an archer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.65,0:14:56.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（冬顔）\Nあの女 弓使いだ　侮るな！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.70,0:14:56.88,Kingdom-Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.59,0:15:00.01,Kingdom-Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,That board's in the way! Move around to the sides!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.62,0:15:00.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（冬顔）板がジャマだ　側面に回れ\N（騎兵）はっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.01,0:15:00.80,Kingdom-Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.03,0:15:04.32,Kingdom-Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,Got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.15,0:15:03.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（騎兵）もらった！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.17,0:15:07.48,Kingdom-Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,Tian Bu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.26,0:15:08.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,天布！\N（天布）はっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.38,0:15:12.26,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,Zi Xia!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.43,0:15:13.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,紫夏！\N（紫夏）見るな！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.61,0:15:13.76,Kingdom-Flashback,Xia,0,0,0,,Don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.54,0:15:22.68,Kingdom-Thought,Zheng,0,0,0,,Zi... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.28,0:15:29.36,Kingdom-Flashback,Zi,0,0,0,,Not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.62,0:15:33.22,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,That's enough! Just sit right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.65,0:15:33.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もういい　そのまま じっとしてろ\N（紫夏）えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.00,0:15:36.88,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,Please, stay still!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.19,0:15:36.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頼むから じっとしていてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.41,0:15:39.16,Kingdom-Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,L-Lord Dong Yan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.42,0:15:42.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,と… 冬顔さま！\N前方に砂煙が上がっております！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.16,0:15:42.10,Kingdom-Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,There is a sand cloud up ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.10,0:15:44.04,Kingdom-Flashback,Dong,0,0,0,,A mounted unit from the State of Qin, eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.13,0:15:47.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,秦国の騎馬隊か！ 政を迎えに\N国境を越えてきおったな？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.20,0:15:47.79,Kingdom-Flashback,Dong,0,0,0,,So they crossed the state border to get Zheng, did they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.97,0:15:49.78,Kingdom-Flashback,Dong,0,0,0,,But they're still far away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.10,0:15:51.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが まだ遠い　遊びは終わりだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.78,0:15:51.35,Kingdom-Flashback,Dong,0,0,0,,It's time to stop playing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.34,0:15:54.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,馬車に乗り移り\N政の首を取ってこい！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.35,0:15:54.66,Kingdom-Flashback,Dong,0,0,0,,Board that carriage and take Zheng's head!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.66,0:15:56.38,Kingdom-Flashback,Guys,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.19,0:16:03.43,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:05.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜだ？ なぜ そこまで…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.21,0:16:05.78,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,Why are you going so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.09,0:16:12.20,Kingdom-Flashback,Xia,0,0,0,,When I was young, my life was saved by a complete stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.29,0:16:12.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（紫夏）私も幼いころ\N赤の他人に命懸けで助けられた
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.16,0:16:22.70,Kingdom-Flashback,Xia,0,0,0,,And when I was 10, that man died trying to save yet another person!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.29,0:16:18.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その人は 私が10歳のとき
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.06,0:16:22.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,また別の人間を救おうとして\N命を落とした
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.60,0:16:24.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オリャー！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.90,0:16:32.21,Kingdom-Flashback,Xia,0,0,0,,In that man's dying moments, he screamed for me not to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.04,0:16:32.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その人の死に際 私は\N“死なないでくれ”と泣き叫んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.64,0:16:37.31,Kingdom-Flashback,Xia,0,0,0,,And I haven't still haven't done a single thing to repay the debt he gave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.98,0:16:37.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“受けた恩に対し 私は まだ\N何ひとつ返せていない”と
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.06,0:16:43.82,Kingdom-Flashback,Xia,0,0,0,,But that man...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.15,0:16:43.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし その人は…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.42,0:16:52.11,Kingdom-Thought,Dad,0,0,0,,Favors should always be passed on to another person.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.53,0:16:52.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（父親）恩恵は全て 次の者へ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.96,0:16:59.48,Kingdom-Thought,Dad,0,0,0,,My life was saved by the lives of several people as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.13,0:16:58.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（父親）私の命も\N幾人かの命によって救われてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.48,0:17:04.48,Kingdom-Thought,Dad,0,0,0,,I've intended to pay back that entire debt to you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.50,0:17:04.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その恩を余さず\Nお前たちに注いだつもりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.37,0:17:11.58,Kingdom-Thought,Dad,0,0,0,,Zi Xia, if you're able to do something for someone else in the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.48,0:17:11.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,紫夏… お前が この先\N他人のために何かできたら
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.52,0:17:15.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは\N私にとっても大きな意味を持つ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.58,0:17:15.63,Kingdom-Thought,Dad,0,0,0,,that would mean the world to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.43,0:17:19.76,Kingdom-Thought,Dad,0,0,0,,No matter how small they are...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.55,0:17:19.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どんなに些細(ささい)なことでも
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.76,0:17:22.89,Kingdom-Thought,Dad,0,0,0,,pass on favors to someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.76,0:17:22.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,受けた恩恵を次の者へ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.16,0:17:27.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フフフッ… そういうものだ 紫夏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.84,0:17:27.27,Kingdom-Thought,Dad,0,0,0,,That's how they work, Zi Xia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.10,0:17:29.89,Kingdom-Thought,Dad,0,0,0,,If you do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.20,0:17:29.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうやって…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.31,0:17:33.31,Kingdom-Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,Out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.54,0:17:33.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（騎兵）どけ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.38,0:17:37.34,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,Zi Xia!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.44,0:17:38.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,紫夏！\N（紫夏）見るな！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.34,0:17:38.44,Kingdom-Flashback,Xia,0,0,0,,Don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.96,0:17:52.46,Kingdom-Flashback,Xia,0,0,0,,If you do that... then people... will be bound to one another...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.19,0:17:48.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（紫夏）そうやって…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.29,0:17:52.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうやって 人は つながっていく
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.28,0:17:57.50,Kingdom-Flashback,Xia,0,0,0,,That is what I was taught.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.46,0:17:57.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（紫夏）私は そう教えられてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.52,0:18:01.14,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,So... So that's why you helped me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.60,0:18:01.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（政）だから… だから 俺を…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.66,0:18:03.52,Kingdom-Thought,Xia,0,0,0,,That's part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.70,0:18:05.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（紫夏）それもあります\Nでも それだけじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.52,0:18:05.34,Kingdom-Thought,Xia,0,0,0,,But that's not all...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.70,0:18:15.90,Kingdom-Thought,Xia,0,0,0,,I wanted to see the moon I saw with you that day again....
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.71,0:18:15.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（紫夏）あの日見た あの月を\Nもう一度 あなたと…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.87,0:18:26.12,Kingdom-Flashback,Xia,0,0,0,,I won't let you... kill this boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:23.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この子は…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.39,0:18:25.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,殺させない！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.26,0:18:31.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ええい！ 何をしている？ 殺せ！\N（紫夏）殺させない！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.98,0:18:28.46,Kingdom-Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.46,0:18:29.37,Kingdom-Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,Kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.37,0:18:31.12,Kingdom-Flashback,Xia,0,0,0,,I won't let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.63,0:18:35.84,Kingdom-Flashback,Chang,0,0,0,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.67,0:18:37.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いたぞ！ 政さま！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.84,0:18:37.63,Kingdom-Flashback,Chang,0,0,0,,Lord Zheng!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.63,0:18:40.02,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,Zi Xia! It's the State of Qin soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.64,0:18:41.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,紫夏！\N秦国の兵だ！ 助けが来たぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.02,0:18:41.38,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,They're here to save us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.51,0:18:44.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（冬顔）\Nチッ… 女はいい　政を射(う)て！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.31,0:18:45.14,Kingdom-Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,Forget the woman, shoot Zheng!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.88,0:18:50.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頑張れ 紫夏！ もう少しだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.89,0:18:50.77,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Zi Xia! We're almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.65,0:18:52.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やれー！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.77,0:18:52.14,Kingdom-Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.74,0:18:57.40,Kingdom-Thought,Zheng,0,0,0,,Zi Xia! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.79,0:18:57.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,紫夏！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.40,0:18:59.62,Kingdom-Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,What is that woman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.66,0:18:58.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（騎兵）何だ この女！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.56,0:19:02.90,Kingdom-Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.63,0:19:02.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（冬顔）殺せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.16,0:19:09.66,Kingdom-Flashback,Chang,0,0,0,,Lord Zheng!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.40,0:19:09.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,政さま！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.91,0:19:12.45,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,Zi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.91,0:19:24.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,紫夏ーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.92,0:19:25.21,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,Zi Xia!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.53,0:19:40.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハァ… 政さま…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.79,0:19:40.44,Kingdom-Flashback,Zi,0,0,0,,Lord... Zheng...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.58,0:19:42.90,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.67,0:19:42.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.53,0:19:46.89,Kingdom-Flashback,Zi,0,0,0,,Are you... unhurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.67,0:19:46.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（紫夏）おケガはありませんか？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.08,0:19:53.02,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.31,0:19:52.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ 大丈夫だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.94,0:19:55.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前のおかげで 俺は秦へ帰れる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.02,0:19:56.08,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, I'm gonna make it home to Qin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:19:59.64,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, I'm gonna become king.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.55,0:19:59.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（政）\Nお前のおかげで 俺は王になる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.26,0:20:07.84,Kingdom-Flashback,Zi,0,0,0,,I'd feel bad... if you forgot about Dao Jian... and the others...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.49,0:20:07.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,道剣どのたちのことも\N忘れては かわいそう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.84,0:20:10.22,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,Yeah. You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.19,0:20:09.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.22,0:20:15.30,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,Dao Jian, Dan Yuan, Tian Ci, Ya Men, Jiang Zhao...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.26,0:20:16.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,道剣 単元 田慈 亜門 江彰\Nみんなのおかげだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.30,0:20:17.06,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,It was thanks to all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.82,0:20:20.56,Kingdom-Flashback,Xia,0,0,0,,Lord Zheng...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.20,0:20:21.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,政さま\N（政）うん？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.75,0:20:24.92,Kingdom-Flashback,Xia,0,0,0,,Due to the bad luck of your birth,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.81,0:20:24.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（紫夏）\Nあなたは生まれの不運により…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.84,0:20:28.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,およそ王族が歩まぬ道を歩まされた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.92,0:20:29.04,Kingdom-Flashback,Xia,0,0,0,,you walked a path that almost no member of a royal family has walked...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:39.63,Kingdom-Flashback,Xia,0,0,0,,But, because of those difficult experiences, there is no person like you who will become a king.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.95,0:20:31.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ですが…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.85,0:20:36.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたほどつらい経験をして\N王になる方は…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.46,0:20:39.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほかにいません
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.32,0:20:43.59,Kingdom-Flashback,Xia,0,0,0,,So... I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.43,0:20:43.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（紫夏）だから きっと…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.09,0:20:51.39,Kingdom-Flashback,Xia,0,0,0,,You will... become a king greater than any other.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.33,0:20:51.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたは\N誰よりも偉大な王になれます
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.91,0:20:58.61,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,Zi Xia! Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.91,0:20:57.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,紫夏！ くそ…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.58,0:21:00.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くそー！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.61,0:21:00.59,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.98,0:21:03.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（紫夏）政さま…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.00,0:21:06.50,Kingdom-Flashback,Xia,0,0,0,,Lord Zheng... your face...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.95,0:21:06.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お顔を…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.72,0:21:11.41,Kingdom-Flashback,Xia,0,0,0,,Your eyes... are no longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.79,0:21:11.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう目が…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.03,0:21:19.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（紫夏）\Nああ… つきものは落ちましたなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.29,0:21:19.94,Kingdom-Flashback,Xia,0,0,0,,It looks like the moon has set.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.83,0:21:21.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,瞳が なんとも…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.94,0:21:25.62,Kingdom-Flashback,Xia,0,0,0,,Your eyes are... so beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.27,0:21:25.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,美しい…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.69,0:21:46.00,Kingdom-Flashback,Zheng,0,0,0,,Zi Xia!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.39,0:21:45.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（政）紫夏ーっ！
